description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

In our kick off episode, Corinne shares her story of obesity and exactly what you need to do to start your own success story. You also meet her co-host, Kathy, who has lost 75lbs. since meeting Corinne.

You will learn how to make commitments to yourself you will actually keep and how the smallest steps will be the biggest ones in your weightloss.
